  m_text: "The bucket goblin is similar to the regular goblin in its behaviour patterns,
    however do not be fooled! It has found the solution to the regular's one weakness...\nby
    putting a bucket on its head! \nYour attacks will not reach this goblin due to
    its strategic (yet charming) choice of apparel, \nyou will need to cut it out
    of the rink along with the ice under its feet!"
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
  m_fontAsset: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 8f586378b4e144a9851e7b34d9b748ee, type: 2}
  m_sharedMaterial: {fileID: 2180264, guid: 8f586378b4e144a9851e7b34d9b748ee, type: 2}
