  m_text: 'The ranged goblin is the pinnacle of goblin evolution, as it knows that
    getting too close can be dangerous.

    Therefore it will keep it''s distance
    while launching snowballs towards you.

    When the snowball lands, it will
    create a gaping hole in the ice!'
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
  m_fontAsset: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 8f586378b4e144a9851e7b34d9b748ee, type: 2}
