  m_text: 'The regular goblin will follow you throughout your ice skating shenanigans,
    attempting to close the gap between you and itself...

    If it manages to get
    close to you, it will attempt to attack with its ferocious stick!

    If the
    attack lands, you will take damage and succumb to the goblin...'
